data.description: Great Location in the Moors Hialeah, a gated community with 24/7 security, clubhouse, 2 community pools, tennis courts, gym. The location is ideal, with easy access to highways, shopping centers, restaurants, & entertainment. The property is well maintained, tile floors through out the house. Good size backyard with a shed and mango tree. 1 Car garage and can park 2 cars in the drive way. Come check it out.
